1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:00,840
¿Quién deja

2
00:00:00,840 --> 00:00:01,320
una mesa así

3
00:00:01,320 --> 00:00:02,000
en la calle?

4
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:02,480
Negra,

5
00:00:02,480 --> 00:00:03,120
sin un rasguño,

6
00:00:03,120 --> 00:00:03,560
ahí plantada

7
00:00:03,560 --> 00:00:04,280
en Exposición.

8
00:00:04,280 --> 00:00:04,920
Quedaos

9
00:00:04,920 --> 00:00:06,000
que esto tiene miga.

10
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:06,800
Si quien la dejó

11
00:00:06,800 --> 00:00:07,440
hubiera sabido

12
00:00:07,440 --> 00:00:08,760
que alguien la quería...

13
00:00:08,760 --> 00:00:09,720
no estaría aquí.

14
00:00:09,720 --> 00:00:10,440
Eso es lo que pasa

15
00:00:10,440 --> 00:00:11,080
cuando no hay

16
00:00:11,080 --> 00:00:11,840
una forma fácil

17
00:00:11,840 --> 00:00:12,880
de compartir.

18
00:00:12,880 --> 00:00:13,520
Las cosas acaban

19
00:00:13,520 --> 00:00:14,120
en la acera

20
00:00:14,120 --> 00:00:14,800
en vez de en casa

21
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:15,240
de alguien.

22
00:00:15,240 --> 00:00:16,280
Pues fijaos

23
00:00:16,280 --> 00:00:16,960
lo fácil que es

24
00:00:16,960 --> 00:00:17,760
cambiar esto.

25
00:00:17,760 --> 00:00:18,720
Con Givore

26
00:00:18,720 --> 00:00:19,320
hago una foto,

27
00:00:19,320 --> 00:00:19,960
escribo qué es,

28
00:00:19,960 --> 00:00:20,840
y se publica

29
00:00:20,840 --> 00:00:21,400
para todo el que

30
00:00:21,400 --> 00:00:22,160
esté cerca.

31
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:22,720
No tardo ni

32
00:00:22,720 --> 00:00:23,280
lo que dura

33
00:00:23,280 --> 00:00:24,640
un semáforo en rojo.

34
00:00:24,640 --> 00:00:25,560
Y funciona.

35
00:00:25,560 --> 00:00:26,280
La gente lo ve,

36
00:00:26,280 --> 00:00:27,120
le interesa,

37
00:00:27,120 --> 00:00:27,960
y aparece.

38
00:00:27,960 --> 00:00:28,640
Hoy esa mesa

39
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:28,840
ya no está

40
00:00:28,840 --> 00:00:29,720
en la acera.

41
00:00:29,720 --> 00:00:31,040
Está en un salón.

42
00:00:31,040 --> 00:00:32,040
Antes de tirar algo,

43
00:00:32,040 --> 00:00:33,720
pensad si alguien más

44
00:00:33,720 --> 00:00:35,040
lo puede aprovechar.

45
00:00:35,040 --> 00:00:35,600
A lo mejor está

46
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:36,200
más cerca

47
00:00:36,200 --> 00:00:37,000
de lo que creéis.

